import React from 'react';
import { Container, Screen, Previous, Current, Button } from './Styled'


export default function Calculator() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Screen>
                <Previous></Previous>
                <Current></Current>
            </Screen>
            <Button gridSpan={2}>AC</Button>
            <Button>DEL</Button>
            <Button operation>รท</Button>
            <Button>7</Button>
            <Button>8</Button>
            <Button>9</Button>
            <Button operation>x</Button>
            <Button>4</Button>
            <Button>5</Button>
            <Button>6</Button>
            <Button operation>+</Button>
            <Button>1</Button>
            <Button>2</Button>
            <Button>3</Button>
            <Button operation>-</Button>
            <Button>.</Button>
            <Button>0</Button>
            <Button gridSpan={2} >=</Button>
            

        </Container>
        
    )
}
